data.description: Welcome to this stunning home nestled on a cul-de-sac lot! This beautifully maintained property offers a range of desirable features, including granite counters, new windows, and stainless steel appliances. The open floor plan creates a spacious and inviting atmosphere, complemented by a charming corner stone fireplace. Outside, you'll find a private fenced backyard, providing the perfect space for relaxation and entertaining. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional home yours! Close to beaches, downtown, town center, highways, schools, restaurants, stores, hospitals and more!
